# Code owners for prisma/app.
#
# Every PR auto-routes to the maintainer team for review. If branch
# protection on `main` requires an approving review from a code owner,
# the team below must exist and have write access to this repo.
#
# NOTE: verify this team slug is correct for prisma/app before
# enabling code-owner-required branch protection — it is carried over
# from prisma-next and may need to change.
#
# This is intentionally a flat ownership rule: until the maintainer
# group is large enough to warrant subsystem-level routing, a single
# rule is easier to keep current than per-directory rules that drift.

* @prisma/ORM-TS-Maintain
